-- Customer references CreditCard and Order directly\nCustomer -> [1-n] Order, [1-n] CreditCard\n\n-- Order does not directly reference CreditCard but has relationships through Payments\nOrder -> [1-n] Payment\n\n-- Payment acts as an intermediary entity linking Orders and CreditCards\nPayment -> [1-1] Order, [1-1] CreditCard  // Unique constraint on Order if only one CC per order should be allowed\n\n-- CreditCard references Customer directly\nCreditCard -> [1-n] Customer